![image](https://i.ibb.co/N7WFSSj/Pics-Art-06-20-06-00-09.png) = The New ZeroWiki = This is a clone of [[ZeroWiki]] created with better organization and information-richness in mind. [[ZeroWiki]] is a wiki platform for [[ZeroNet]], the distributed web network based on [[BitTorrent]], [[Bitcoin]] and [[Tor]]. [[ZeroWiki]] is public and [[cloning|clonable]]. Wikis can be used for taking notes, storing snippets, sharing knowledge by creating [[FAQ]]s and documentations, keeping track of your goals, or as simple to-do lists. See the [[help|help page]] for a more in-depth view of how it works.

Some typical yields

Crop

L/ha

Palm oil1

Coconut

Cyperus esculentus2

Rapeseed3

Soy (Indiana)4

Chinese tallow56

Peanut7

Sunflower8

Hemp

# 0list | [[ZeroNet]]

[0list](/0list.bit/), also know as ZeroList, is an index for [[zites]]. It is a kind of forum, cloned from [[ZeroTalk]].

Maintained by community and not moderated, many sites are specified several times on 0list. It has no searching features as well.

In 2017, this was replaced by [[ZeroSites]].
